I punched a hole in the dash to put in a cigarette lighter, so I could 
power a tire inflator,
etc, but for a straight USB, I'd consider something like this Neutrik 
connector.
This requires the same 15/16in hole punch as the cigarette lighter.  A 
greenlee punch
for the hole was about $30.

http://www.bhphotovideo.com/c/product/561202-REG/Neutrik_NAUSB_W_B_NAUSB_B_USB_Female_Type_A.html

